Kanungo Institute of Diabetes Specialities (KIDS) is a diabetes multi-speciality hospital in Bhubaneswar, India. KIDS is named after its Founder & Chairman Dr.Alok Kanungo, a diabetologist of international repute.KIDS is a research based institute and has research-intensive collaborations with:
Karolinska Institutet, Sweden
National Institutes of Health, United States
Institute of Life Sciences, Bhubaneswar, India
National Institute of Science Education and Research, Bhubaneswar, India


